summary: LETTER FROM  DENNIS ENOCH, PARTNER OF VM BOAT TRAILERS. MR. ENOCH  OPPOSES THOSE PROVISIONS OF EARLY WARNING REPORTING (EWR) REGULATIONS THAT REQUIRE OVER 500 SMALL TO MEDIUM TRAILER MANUFACTURERS TO SUBMIT COMPREHENSIVEM EARLY WARNING REPORTS TO NHTSA. MR ENOCH  HAS INSISTED THAT SUCH REGULATIONS WOULD PUT HIM AND SOME OF HIS COLLEAGUES OUT OF BUSINESS.  *AK
